it was very easy to make this recipe vegan (containing no animal-derived ingredients) by substituting nondairy margarine for the unsalted butter and Ener-G brand egg replacer in lieu of the egg. because the margarine i used was salted, i reduced the salt slightly (1/2 tsp plus a pinch). The cookies were fantastic.

