Rating: 4
These turned out exactly like the picture. They flavor was ginger-y but not too spicy/more sweet. Perfect. The crystallized ginger I purchased was in large pieces that needed to be chopped. It stuck together as I chopped it and didn't incorporate nicely into the flour mixture, but I solved this by putting the crystallized ginger in my food processor with the flour mixture (1st 6 ingredients). This whipped it around enough to sufficiently chop the ingredients but also to combine with the dry mixture evenly.

