Can't find molasses in Costa Rica as well. I used 1/3 part palm sugar to 2/3 parts dark corn syrup to equal 1/4c of molasses. To those who use all butter instead of recommended mix of shortening: The cookies will be more buttery but also crisper. The recommended mix imparts a chewier and softer cookie but still has butter flavor.

